gujarati.context:
New era of demons, tenth reincarnation of virtue; 
Eleventh is marriage, thirteenth is devotion's duty;
Twelfth is Ramanand arriving generous as ever.

Know the mystery of fourteenth; 
the measure of the sacrifice is great, they say;
In this world's chaos, find peace in silence, they say;
After eight days, that will be a great gain, they say.

Here is the translation:

Forty people have forty brothers and sisters, who are settled in their village; 
Forty people are the fortunate ones, whose names are written by Pavan.

Forty-nine:

God is satisfied in His own way, He takes care of Himself; 
He is sorrowful in the separation from Hari, the suffering of Hari's people is a disease.

Here is the translation:

He is Piyush to Harijan, he is this pain to those who are facing; 
One gets pleasure from sweet company, says the supreme, one gets pleasure without a tinge of sadness.
